        <abstract>
            <para>The Marion Ownbey Herbarium (WS) is a collection of over 420,000 specimens of vascular plants, bryophytes, and lichens.&amp;nbsp; The herbarium includes plants from around the world, with an emphasis on species from the Inland Pacific Northwest, Northern Rocky Mountains, Great Basin, and California.</para>
        </abstract>
